<qti-assessment-item xmlns="http://www.imsglobal.org/xsd/imsqtiasi_v3p0" xmlns:m="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML" xmlns:xsi="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance" identifier="Q35_v17" title="Q35_v17" time-dependent="false" adaptive="false" xsi:schemaLocation="http://www.imsglobal.org/xsd/imsqtiasi_v3p0 https://purl.imsglobal.org/spec/qti/v3p0/schema/xsd/imsqti_asiv3p0_v1p0.xsd">
  <qti-response-declaration identifier="RESPONSE" cardinality="single" base-type="identifier">
    <qti-correct-response>
      <qti-value>ChoiceB</qti-value>
    </qti-correct-response>
  </qti-response-declaration>
  <qti-outcome-declaration identifier="FEEDBACK" cardinality="single" base-type="identifier"/>
  <qti-outcome-declaration identifier="SOLUTION" cardinality="single" base-type="identifier"/>
  <qti-outcome-declaration identifier="SCORE" cardinality="single" base-type="float"><qti-default-value><qti-value>0</qti-value></qti-default-value></qti-outcome-declaration><qti-item-body>
    <p>La puntuación final S que obtiene un jugador en un juego en línea se calcula mediante la expresión 
      <m:math>
        <m:mi>S</m:mi>
        <m:mo>=</m:mo>
        <m:mn>10</m:mn>
        <m:mo>+</m:mo>
        <m:mfrac>
          <m:mrow>
            <m:mi>m</m:mi>
            <m:mo>−</m:mo>
            <m:mn>40</m:mn>
          </m:mrow>
          <m:mn>7</m:mn>
        </m:mfrac>
      </m:math>,
      donde S es el puntaje final y m el número de misiones completadas. La fórmula suma un puntaje base de 10 puntos y luego agrega una séptima parte de la diferencia entre las misiones realizadas y 40. Si al finalizar una partida un jugador obtuvo un puntaje de 
      <m:math>
        <m:mi>S</m:mi>
        <m:mo>=</m:mo>
        <m:mn>24</m:mn>
      </m:math>, ¿cuántas misiones completó?</p>
    <qti-choice-interaction response-identifier="RESPONSE" shuffle="true" max-choices="1">
      
      <qti-simple-choice identifier="ChoiceA">42<qti-feedback-inline identifier="FB_ChoiceA" outcome-identifier="FEEDBACK">Incorrecto. Si m = 42, entonces S = 10 + (42 − 40)/7 = 10 + 2/7, que no es 24.</qti-feedback-inline></qti-simple-choice>
      <qti-simple-choice identifier="ChoiceB">138<qti-feedback-inline identifier="FB_ChoiceB" outcome-identifier="FEEDBACK">¡Correcto! Si m = 138, entonces S = 10 + (138 − 40)/7 = 10 + 98/7 = 10 + 14 = 24. Por lo tanto, 138 misiones sí produce el puntaje final indicado.</qti-feedback-inline></qti-simple-choice>
      
      <qti-simple-choice identifier="ChoiceC">58<qti-feedback-inline identifier="FB_ChoiceC" outcome-identifier="FEEDBACK">Incorrecto. Si m = 58, entonces S = 10 + (58 − 40)/7 = 10 + 18/7, que no es 24.</qti-feedback-inline></qti-simple-choice>
      
      <qti-simple-choice identifier="ChoiceD">208<qti-feedback-inline identifier="FB_ChoiceD" outcome-identifier="FEEDBACK">Incorrecto. Si m = 208, entonces S = 10 + (208 − 40)/7 = 10 + 168/7 = 10 + 24 = 34, que no es 24.</qti-feedback-inline></qti-simple-choice>
    </qti-choice-interaction>
    <qti-feedback-block identifier="show" outcome-identifier="SOLUTION" show-hide="show">
      <qti-content-body>
        <p><strong>Resolución paso a paso</strong></p>
        <ol>
          <li>
            <p><strong>Paso 1: Sustituir el valor de</strong> <m:math><m:mi>S</m:mi></m:math> <strong>en la fórmula</strong></p>
            <p>La expresión dada es:</p>
            <p>
              <m:math>
                <m:mi>S</m:mi>
                <m:mo>=</m:mo>
                <m:mn>10</m:mn>
                <m:mo>+</m:mo>
                <m:mfrac>
                  <m:mrow>
                    <m:mi>m</m:mi>
                    <m:mo>−</m:mo>
                    <m:mn>40</m:mn>
                  </m:mrow>
                  <m:mn>7</m:mn>
                </m:mfrac>
              </m:math>
            </p>
            <p>Como el jugador obtuvo <m:math><m:mi>S</m:mi><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>24</m:mn></m:math>, se reemplaza:</p>
            <p>
              <m:math>
                <m:mn>24</m:mn>
                <m:mo>=</m:mo>
                <m:mn>10</m:mn>
                <m:mo>+</m:mo>
                <m:mfrac>
                  <m:mrow>
                    <m:mi>m</m:mi>
                    <m:mo>−</m:mo>
                    <m:mn>40</m:mn>
                  </m:mrow>
                  <m:mn>7</m:mn>
                </m:mfrac>
              </m:math>
            </p>
          </li>
          <li>
            <p><strong>Paso 2: Restar 10 en ambos lados</strong></p>
            <p>
              <m:math>
                <m:mn>24</m:mn>
                <m:mo>−</m:mo>
                <m:mn>10</m:mn>
                <m:mo>=</m:mo>
                <m:mfrac>
                  <m:mrow>
                    <m:mi>m</m:mi>
                    <m:mo>−</m:mo>
                    <m:mn>40</m:mn>
                  </m:mrow>
                  <m:mn>7</m:mn>
                </m:mfrac>
              </m:math>
            </p>
            <p>
              <m:math>
                <m:mn>14</m:mn>
                <m:mo>=</m:mo>
                <m:mfrac>
                  <m:mrow>
                    <m:mi>m</m:mi>
                    <m:mo>−</m:mo>
                    <m:mn>40</m:mn>
                  </m:mrow>
                  <m:mn>7</m:mn>
                </m:mfrac>
              </m:math>
            </p>
          </li>
          <li>
            <p><strong>Paso 3: Multiplicar ambos lados por 7</strong></p>
            <p>
              <m:math>
                <m:mn>14</m:mn>
                <m:mo>×</m:mo>
                <m:mn>7</m:mn>
                <m:mo>=</m:mo>
                <m:mi>m</m:mi>
                <m:mo>−</m:mo>
                <m:mn>40</m:mn>
              </m:math>
            </p>
            <p>
              <m:math>
                <m:mn>98</m:mn>
                <m:mo>=</m:mo>
                <m:mi>m</m:mi>
                <m:mo>−</m:mo>
                <m:mn>40</m:mn>
              </m:math>
            </p>
          </li>
          <li>
            <p><strong>Paso 4: Sumar 40 en ambos lados</strong></p>
            <p>
              <m:math>
                <m:mn>98</m:mn>
                <m:mo>+</m:mo>
                <m:mn>40</m:mn>
                <m:mo>=</m:mo>
                <m:mi>m</m:mi>
              </m:math>
            </p>
            <p>
              <m:math>
                <m:mn>138</m:mn>
                <m:mo>=</m:mo>
                <m:mi>m</m:mi>
              </m:math>
            </p>
          </li>
          <li>
            <p><strong>Conclusión</strong></p>
            <p>El jugador completó <strong>138 misiones</strong>, por lo tanto la alternativa correcta es <strong>B</strong>.</p>
          </li>
          <li>
            <p><strong>Comprobación</strong></p>
            <p>
              <m:math>
                <m:mi>S</m:mi>
                <m:mo>=</m:mo>
                <m:mn>10</m:mn>
                <m:mo>+</m:mo>
                <m:mfrac>
                  <m:mrow>
                    <m:mn>138</m:mn>
                    <m:mo>−</m:mo>
                    <m:mn>40</m:mn>
                  </m:mrow>
                  <m:mn>7</m:mn>
                </m:mfrac>
              </m:math>
            </p>
            <p>
              <m:math>
                <m:mi>S</m:mi>
                <m:mo>=</m:mo>
                <m:mn>10</m:mn>
                <m:mo>+</m:mo>
                <m:mfrac>
                  <m:mn>98</m:mn>
                  <m:mn>7</m:mn>
                </m:mfrac>
                <m:mo>=</m:mo>
                <m:mn>10</m:mn>
                <m:mo>+</m:mo>
                <m:mn>14</m:mn>
                <m:mo>=</m:mo>
                <m:mn>24</m:mn>
              </m:math>
            </p>
          </li>
        </ol>
      </qti-content-body>
    </qti-feedback-block>
  </qti-item-body>
  <qti-response-processing>
    <qti-response-condition>
      <qti-response-if>
        <qti-match>
          <qti-variable identifier="RESPONSE"/>
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">ChoiceB</qti-base-value>
        </qti-match>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="SCORE">
          <qti-base-value base-type="float">1</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="FEEDBACK">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">FB_ChoiceB</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="SOLUTION">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">show</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
      </qti-response-if>
      <qti-response-else-if>
        <qti-match>
          <qti-variable identifier="RESPONSE"/>
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">ChoiceA</qti-base-value>
        </qti-match>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="FEEDBACK">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">FB_ChoiceA</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="SOLUTION">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">show</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
      </qti-response-else-if>
      <qti-response-else-if>
        <qti-match>
          <qti-variable identifier="RESPONSE"/>
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">ChoiceC</qti-base-value>
        </qti-match>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="FEEDBACK">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">FB_ChoiceC</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="SOLUTION">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">show</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
      </qti-response-else-if>
      <qti-response-else-if>
        <qti-match>
          <qti-variable identifier="RESPONSE"/>
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">ChoiceD</qti-base-value>
        </qti-match>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="FEEDBACK">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">FB_ChoiceD</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="SOLUTION">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">show</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
      </qti-response-else-if>
      <qti-response-else>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="FEEDBACK">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">FB_ChoiceA</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="SOLUTION">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">show</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
      </qti-response-else>
    </qti-response-condition>
  </qti-response-processing>
</qti-assessment-item>